com.stormpath.sdk.application.webconfig

Interface MeExpansionConfig


  • public interface MeExpansionConfig
    The MeExpansionConfig belongs to a MeConfig and exposes the expandable properties of an Account returned when accessing the /me route with the proper assertion.
    Since:
    1.2.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
